de Paul medical clinic, looks over a prescription. The clinic relies on 
volunteer help from doctors and nurses to provide primary health care to the 
homeless and other needy people. Experts welcome the assistance but say the 
problem is so acute that more than voluntarism is needed. VINCE COMPAGNONE / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
