<HEADLINE>
<P>
ON THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"We are in an environment where people overreact to short-term stimuli because 
very few have any long-term convictions anymore. This is about as nervous a 
market as I've ever seen." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Michael Metz, chief market analyst with Oppenheimer &amp; Co., on last 
week's stock market slide. 
</P>
</TEXT>
