<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE L.A. COFFEEHOUSE SCENE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By KEVIN ALLMAN 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ESPRESSO BAR: 34 S. Raymond Ave., Pasadena. (818) 356-9095. 
</P>
<P>
Hours: Monday to Thursday, noon to 1 a.m.; Friday and Saturday, noon to 2 a.m.; 
Sunday, noon to midnight. 
</P>
