rebounds, and Anthony Avent hit a three-point shot with a minute to go in East 
Rutherford, N.J., to lift the Pirates to a Big East Conference victory. 
</P>
<P>
It was the second win in a row for the Pirates (10-7, 3-4). Villanova (10-11, 
3-5), made just 16 of 61 shots. 
</P>
