</P>
<P>
* Back to the Future: Scheduled to open in 1992. 
</P>
<P>
* Shopping: MCA Inc. expected to break ground in September for a quarter-mile 
shopping street at Universal City that will connect the 18-screen Cineplex 
Odeon with the studio tour entrance and two restaurants. 
</P>
