star Shadoe Stevens. The show has been put on hiatus until March. RANDY 
LEFFINGWELL / L.A. Times; Photo, Hargrove's series -- "Max Monroe,"; Photo, 
"Perry Mason,"; Photo, "Matlock,"; Photo, "Jake and the Fatman"; Photo, and 
"Father Dowling Mysteries." 
</P>
